{"tid":391644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"外國讀書讀到好大壓力,好辛苦…","createTime":"2017-09-08T02:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T11:06:00.000Z","uid":145086,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ae0a9a042b453cda6af36447ad91a17996c2b6a","tid":391644,"uid":145086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"可能有少少長<br />\n希望咁多位睇完覆下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實關感情事<br />\n<br />\n我本來係外國讀緊cc 今年year2<br />\n成績都ok啦 唔算太差又唔係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說我岩岩同女朋友分左手大約個半月左右<br />\n分既原因係因為佢有第二個<br />\n分左個陣仲係香港,仲未返外國<br />\n個陣已經日日喊,野都食唔到<br />\n輕左10lbs左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來心情好左啲架啦<br />\n<br />\n好啦 返到外國(我同ex同city讀書）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢現任都係呢度附近<br />\n佢竟然一時話好掛住我 仲鍾意我 一時又幾日唔理我<br />\n對我忽冷忽熱咁 <br />\n我分唔清楚佢係當我水泡玩具吊住我<br />\n定係佢仲鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我係一個好重感情既人&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我比佢搞到日日行屍走肉咁<br />\n開左學兩星期 我日日上堂都集中唔到精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好擔心keep住呢個心態上堂<br />\n我gpa一定跌穿3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我好想振作架&hellip;但一諗起佢 我個人又沉返<br />\n究竟佢想點,同佢男朋友一齊點解仲要話掛住我<br />\n問佢二揀一 佢又話唔好逼佢<br />\n究竟佢係咪純粹吊住我,當我玩具&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我好想忘記佢 focus係學業上面<br />\n但我做唔到呀&hellip;<br />\n唔好話gym sport 搵朋友傾呢啲&hellip;<br />\n我全部做哂都係冇用&hellip; 成個腦海都係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你同你男朋友一齊咪好囉&hellip;點解要耐唔耐吊我一下喎 <br />\n我做錯啲咩&hellip;你要咁樣對我,走咪走囉 你搞咁多野想點<br />\n<br />\nBtw我英國jj"},{"pid":"489fa1a2b168208c597281fe4030189dfb259eb9","tid":391644,"uid":145086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"老實講 大家曾經都係大家最愛<br />\n點解要咁吊住我先<br />\n係咪見到我咁你好快樂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07903d62ebf5f44c65bb9b590416e10b100f4e5","tid":391644,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"女人只係for fun 男人人生目標係自己夢想"},{"pid":"71a96f7fbfb38725e5d37d796d180c9aa21e0017","tid":391644,"uid":145086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"開左學三個禮拜&hellip;<br />\n我比佢搞到我冇哂心機讀書啦&hellip;<br />\nQuiz都做得唔好&hellip;再係咁我爛硬gpa...."},{"pid":"74c7ba1584807a260dfce14d4ad2d46ed9e629cb","tid":391644,"uid":145086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人只係for fun 男人人生目標係自己夢想</blockquote><br />\n我明白男人唔應該為呢啲放棄自己<br />\n但問題我係感情問題上我係好感性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我釋懷唔到自己"},{"pid":"32599d14a3a42276f2e484c73fbfca4d08055681","tid":391644,"uid":145086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"老實講你估我唔知佢想吊住我咋嘛<br />\n但我放唔低嘛"},{"pid":"d6ed48bd32d46d6f987a3399ae48248049d8eb13","tid":391644,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"針囉 唔針就繼續讀書<br />\n女人冇咗有幾閒？"},{"pid":"923d9eb853ee12d60cddbec53c8993af506c03bc","tid":391644,"uid":39842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"你save 低你自己呢個post !  過多一斷時間再睇番！你會覺得自己好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你個ex 根本兩個都唔愛，佢愛自己咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1714ec70a92fb8ca71cce910ff81e2f84244e54","tid":391644,"uid":131731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"拎得起 放得低 向前看<br />\n長大啦, 唔好將一個唔要你既女仔當左係你世界既全部"},{"pid":"05e11961429727918d497fb641bbf4707e2c7279","tid":391644,"uid":145086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:57:04.000Z","m